I need to convert the Decimal types to numbers in the order object before passing it to the PurchaseTracking component, similar to how it's done for the OrderReceipt component.

---FILEPATH /home/tariqul/Projects/natural-sefa-v2/app/(root)/receipt/[id]/page.tsx
---FIND
```
  return (
    <main className="py-10">
      <PurchaseTracking product={order} />
```
---REPLACE
```
  return (
    <main className="py-10">
      <PurchaseTracking
        product={{
          ...order,
          subtotal: Number(order.subtotal),
          shippingTotal: Number(order.shippingTotal),
          total: Number(order.total),
          items: order.items.map((it) => ({
            ...it,
            unitPrice: Number(it.unitPrice),
            total: Number(it.total),
          })),
        }}
      />
```
---COMPLETE
